er Gesellschaft wir eigentlich leben.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aArchitecturexSociological aspectsxStudy and teaching. 0aArchitekturxSoziologie. 0aSociologyxStudy and teaching. 4aArchitektur. 4aEinführung. 4aGesellschaft. 4aRaum. 4aSoziologie. 4aSoziologische Theorie. 4aUrban Studies. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / Urban.2bisacsh  aIntroduction.  aSociety.  aSociological Theory.  aSociology.  aSpace.  aUrban Studies.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Sozialw. 2000-2009z9783110463392oZDB-23-TSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839410318zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839410318423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839410318/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2000d2009  aZDB-23-TSWc2000d2009